Reset Operate
Phenomenon




Light
Switch three times in a row
Flashing lights


Socket
Press and hold the switch for 3s
The socket indicator flashes quickly


Gateway
Press and hold the switch for 3s
Red and blue lights flash fast


Low-power devices
Press and hold the switch for 3s
Press again to display a long light to configure the network, and the network configuration must be completed during the light is on


Alarm
Press and hold the switch for 3s
Flashing lights



The device in reset state has a default name is out_of_mesh and a default password is 123456.
